<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>Accompaniment – Acappella.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>Pace: Slowly, with feeling.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
