<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>They’re the providence of the Tribunal to us,<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>Their pelts keep Northmen warm…<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
