<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>There is a fourth verse concerning the proliferation of woolly spiders in
the Northlands, but I have deemed it inappropriate to repeat it here.<span
style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>It is quite obscene.<span
style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Besides, I seriously doubt that hairy spider
legs COULD be used for THAT purpose.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'><span style='mso-tab-count:1'>                </span>“Skels” is short for
“Skeletons”, a reference to the legions of undead that walk the canyons of
Everfrost.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
