<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>Is it skill?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Is it luck?<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
line'>We don’t really **** * ****<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none'><span style='layout-grid-mode:
